@node History "History"


V0.1▀   94-Mar-99, Second release, still an unfinnished
        product.
        I just released this, because I know a couple
        of people out there are using the previous ver-
        sion, and they might want the bugfixes.

        Still didnt start the WYSIWYG class.

        ░ The 'changes made' image wouldnt update after
          a save, FIXED.

        ░ The 'save' function would sometimes forget to
          add a '/' between the path and the filename.

        ░ The texteditor will use it's fixed font (if one
          is specified in mui prefs, anyway)
          This should be make it easier to edit guides,
          since they are normally displayd with a fixed font.

        ░ Compiled for 68000 and with optimizing on,
          mostly for fun.

V0.0▀    First release. Prerelease of a pretty unfinnished product.
@ENDNODE

